      <div class="col-md-8 card-body">
        <p class="card-text">
          Welcome! My name is Abigail, I'm a software developer who enjoys helping others boost their project ideas.
          <br>
          My experience for the time being has mostly been creating applications for small businesses, like an e-commerce website and inventory management system.
          I'm mostly interested in web development, interface design and project management. I'm excited to keep learning new technologies to complement and enhance the projects I work on.
