              <span class="font-weight-bold">Freelance Work:</span> Developing an e-commerce website for Ventas Gerizim business. 
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Role:</span> Fullstack developer. 
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Technologies:</span> Laravel 8, MySql, Apache.
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block p-2">
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Intern Student:</span> Improving and correcting existing functionality in a specific module for MOPT in collaboration with an engineer at the institution.
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Role:</span> Backend developer. 
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Technologies:</span> ASP.NET, SQL Server.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block p-2">
              Systems Engineering Bachelor's Degree <br>
              <span class="font-weight-bold">Universidad Nacional de Costa Rica.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block p-2">
